                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character latches onto anything pleasurable\u2014mead, dice games, or even chewing sourleaf\u2014until it\u2019s a crutch they can\u2019t drop. They\u2019ll drain the tavern\u2019s kegs while swearing it\u2019s their last cup. Moderation is a myth to them, and it muddies their focus. Willpower bends under their cravings.",
